description: Conferencia Latinoamericana sobre Municiones de Racimo

subproject.description: The purpose of this project is to facilitate a forum of discussion and analysis among specialists from the Ministries of Foreign Relations and the Ministries of Defense/Public Safety regarding the theme of cluster munitions, aimed at prohibiting the use, production, transfer and stockpiling of cluster munitions that cause unacceptable harm to civilians
